{"title":"Öökreem","description":"","products":[{"product_id":"organic-night-cream-50ml","title":"Vielö Organic Night Cream 50ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eRich organic night cream to intensely hydrate and nourish the skin overnight and stimulate skin regeneration.\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eCreated with organic whey (nourishing), rosehip seed oil (soothing), hyaluronic acid (hydrating), wheat germ oil (protecting) and organic extracts of chamomile (antiseptic), arnica (anti-inflammatory) and mallow (protecting).\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eSuitable for all skin types, also for dry and sensitive skin.\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to Use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Massage gently into freshly cleansed skin and neck. Use it in the evening and whenever your skin needs rich hydration.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Lactis Serum Proteinum**, Rosa Canina Fruit Oil**, Triticum Vulgare (Wheat) Germ Oil**, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil**, Glycerin**, Cera Alba**, Polyglyceryl-3 Polyricinoleate*, Aqua*, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter**, Sorbitan Sesquioleate*, Oenothera Biennis Oil**, Sodium Levulinate*, Glyceryl Caprylate*, Polyglyceryl-3 Ricinoleate, Sodium Hyaluronate*, Sodium Anisate, Tocopherol*, Citric Acid*, Potassium Sorbate, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Oil**, Salvia Officinalis Oil**, Citronellol**\/***, Pelargonium Graveolens Flower Oil**, Malva Sylvestris Flower Extract**, Viola Tricolor Extract**, Matricaria Chamomilla Flower Extract**, Arnica Montana Flower Extract**, Polyglyceryl-4 Caprate*, Geraniol**\/***, Salvia Officinalis Leaf Extract**, Sodium Lactate*, Limonene**\/***, Citral**\/***.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e* from natural origin (99,3%)\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e** certified organic (89,2%)\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e*** from natural essential oils\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHandmade in Austria\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eInspired by circular economy, Vielö refines a high-quality by-product of cheese production, liquid organic whey, and uses it to create certified organic and sustainable skin and body care products. \u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"vielö","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49093459968327,"sku":null,"price":59.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/vielo-organic-night-cream-50ml-212703.jpg?v=1739897344"},{"product_id":"hej-sensitive-24h-cream-50ml","title":"HEJ Organic Organic Sensitive 24h Face Cream 50ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSimply a delicate all-rounder that provides intensive moisture and ensures radiant skin. Rich and quickly absorbed texture ensures that the skin feels pleasant, no matter what time of day.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePromotes the balance of your skin barrier and deeply hydrates\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eQuickly absorbed texture\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNatural power active ingredient complex made from hemp oil, oat and chamomile extract\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSkin type: Especially for sensitive skin\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAllergen-reduced perfume oil, 100% vegan and natural\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eHemp Oil\u003c\/span\u003e contains important Omega-6 fatty acids, promotes cell regeneration and protects the skin without feeling greasy.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eOat Extract\u003c\/span\u003e has an anti-inflammatory and calming effect and is particularly suitable for sensitive skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eChamomile Flower Water\u003c\/span\u003e has soothing and antibacterial characteristics and provides intensive hydration to the skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply to your face morning and evening after cleansing\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Prunus Armeniaca Kernel Oil, Glycerin, Polyglyceryl-3 Dicitrate\/Stearate, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil*, Cetearyl Alcohol, Distarch Phosphate, Cannabis Sativa Seed Oil*, Hydrogenated Rapeseed Oil, Candelilla Cera, Chamomilla Recutita Flower Extract*, Hypericum Perforatum Extract*, Avena Sativa Kernel Extract*, Xanthan Gum, Sodium Levulinate, Sodium Anisate, Alcohol, Tocopherol, Citric Acid, Parfum** *ingredients from certified organic agriculture, **natural essential oils\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eOrganic | Cruelty Free | Vegan | Natural Resources\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Hej","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49509036327239,"sku":"","price":17.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hej-organic-organic-sensitive-24h-face-cream-50ml-375353.png?v=1739897235"},{"product_id":"madara-sos-sensitive-moisturiser-50ml-copy","title":"MÁDARA SOS+ Sensitive Night Cream 70ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eThis intense night cream soothes sensitive, easily irritated and redness-prone skin. With extract of algea, hyaluronic acid and jojoba oil, the non-greasy formula works to balance the skin's microbiome and reinforce its lipid barrier. Helps reduce skin reactivity, redness and burning.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply to clean face, neck and décolleté every evening. Use in combination with MÁDARA SOS+ Sensitive Moisturiser for the best results.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aloe Barbadensis (Aloe) Leaf Juice, Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil, Glycerin, Pentylene Glycol, Polyglyceryl-3 Stearate, Cetearyl Alcohol, Coco- Caprylate, Dicaprylyl Carbonate, Isoamyl Laurate, Aqua, Hydrolyzed Rhodophyceae Extract, Cellulose, Octyldodecanol, Caprylic\/Capric Triglyceride, Xanthan Gum, Irvingia gabonensis kernel butter, Potassium Hydroxide, Hydrogenated Coco-glycerides, Sodium Hyaluronate, Palmitic acid, Stearic Acid, Tocopherol, Ascorbyl Palmitate, Sodium phytate, Hydrolyzed Hyaluronic Acid\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e* Please note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49858969731399,"sku":null,"price":42.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-sos-sensitive-night-cream-70ml-476299.jpg?v=1739897244"},{"product_id":"naif-nurturing-night-cream-50ml","title":"NAIF Nurturing Night Cream 50ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"css-ss00rg\" data-slate-node=\"element\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eNaïf Nurturing Night Cream contributes to a good night's sleep. The regenerating night cream soothes the skin and supports the natural skin process. Includes almond oil, shea butter and macadamia extract for ultimate hydration and moisture retention. No more dry spots!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe cream absorbs quickly, doesn't stick and doesn't make the skin feel tight. So you don't have to worry when resting your head on your pillow. The night cream is made without mineral oils, microplastics and silicones.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe Naïf regenerating night cream is for every skin type. So also for the most sensitive skin. All Naïf products are vegan, made with a gentle fragrance, are dermatologically tested and do not contain the 26 most common allergens.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eA night cream is best applied if you apply a good, thick amount. Do this on clean, cleansed skin. And don't forget to apply it to the neck and décolleté. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eAqua\/ Water, Prunus Amygdalus Dulcis (Sweet Almond) Oil, Glycerin, Persea Gratissima (Avocado) Oil, Macadamia Integrifolia Seed Oil, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter, Methylpropanediol, Linum Usitatissimum (Linseed) Seed Oil, Cetearyl Alcohol, Cetyl Alcohol, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate, Sucrose Stearate, Tocopherol, Helianthus Annuus, (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Xanthan Gum, Caprylyl Glycol, Phenylpropanol, Parfum\/Fragrance, Citric Acid, Sodium Hydroxide\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTube made from recycled plastic\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50915767255367,"sku":null,"price":23.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-nurturing-night-cream-50ml-623217.png?v=1739897168"},{"product_id":"nurme-neroli-collagen-renewal-night-cream-50ml","title":"NURME Neroli Collagen Renewal Night Cream 50ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eThis night cream deeply moisturizes and nourishes, restoring collagen and elasticity lost due to early signs of aging. High in vitamins C and E, along with passion fruit oil, it hydrates and revitalizes the skin, making it youthful and elastic.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eNeroli oil, derived from bitter orange blossoms, offers powerful antimicrobial and antibacterial properties, making it ideal for acne-prone skin and clogged pores. It regulates sebum production, balancing oily skin. Rich in antioxidants and vitamin E, neroli oil provides anti-aging and anti-acne benefits, reducing inflammation and redness.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis product is packaged in a recyclable polypropylene airless bottle. The airless packaging prevents air exposure, ensuring microbiological purity and extending the shelf life of natural cosmetics.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply to clean skin after other serums or creams. Allow to absorb completely.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Citrus Aurantium Dulcis Flower Water*, Aqua*, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil*, Caprylic\/Capric Triglyceride**, Argania Spinosa Kernel Oil*, Glycerin**, Passiflora Edulis Seed Oil*, Butyrospermum Parkii Butter*, Betain**, Polyglyceryl-3 Methylglucose Distearate**, Glyceryl Stearate**, Cetearyl Alcohol**, Myristyl Myristate**, Sodium Levulinate**, Ascorbyl Palmitate**, Sodium Anisate**, Panthenol*, Benzyl Alcohol**, Tocopherol**, Lactic Acid**, Sodium Hyaluronate**, Allantoin*, Sodium Benzoate**, Potassium Sorbate**, Xanthan Gum**, Hectorite**, Cellulose**, Passiflora Incarnata Extract*, Citrus Aurantium Flower Oil*, Limonene***, Linalool***. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e* Natural origin\u003cbr\u003e** Natural cosmetics approved ingredient\u003cbr\u003e***Occurs naturally in essential oils\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Nurme","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50915905012039,"sku":null,"price":27.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/nurme-neroli-collagen-renewal-night-cream-50ml-207317.jpg?v=1739897174"},{"product_id":"berrichi-age-defence-night-cream-30ml","title":"BERRICHI Age Defence Night Cream 30ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eBerrichi night cream Night works for your skin while you rest. Rich and deeply hydrating, this night cream helps the skin to recover and recover from the day’s challenges, leaving it looking fresh and rested in the morning. It nourishes, hydrates and slows the signs of ageing, leaving skin more supple and plump.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBerrichi  Age Defence Night Cream:\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNourishes and restores, making the skin stronger and more resistant\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSoothes irritated and inflamed skin\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDeep moisturizing effect that keeps the skin soft and supple\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eEvens skin tone, reducing fine lines and wrinkles\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eStimulates blood circulation, helping the skin to regenerate faster\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eMain ingredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eFurcellaran \u003c\/span\u003e– antioxidant, helps to maintain skin moisture balance and strengthen the skin’s protective barrier, slows down the skin’s ageing process, reduces inflammation and dryness. Furtsellaran is obtained from algae grown in Estonian waters.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eAstaxanthin\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e– an antioxidant, the most effective natural anti-ageing agent with the ability to penetrate cell membranes, affecting the skin deeply. Stimulates the production of collagen, balances the skin’s moisture levels, protects the skin from central irritants.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eRetinol\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e– improves skin texture, increases radiance and acts against signs of aging. Retinol accelerates cell healing and skin renewal, increases collagen production, while smoothing out unevenness\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eAloe Vera\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e– antioxidant, antibacterial and anti-inflammatory properties that accelerate healing, moisturise the skin and prevent ageing.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eCacay oil\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e– rich in vitamins A and E. Helps reduce wrinkles and improve skin elasticity, stimulating collagen production and cell renewal.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e Suitable for all skin types\u003c\/span\u003e. Recommended for age 25+\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply to clean skin or apply serum. Use only as a night cream because it contains retinol. The effect of retinol is deactivated by the sun and can make the skin more sensitive to the sun.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Persea Gratissima oil (Organic Avocado oil), Prunus Armeniaca kernel oil (Organic Apricot kernel oil), Caryodendron Orinocense seed oil (Cacay oil), Aleurites Moluccana seed oil (Kukui nut oil), Cetearyl Olivate\/Sorbitan Olivate, Cetearyl Alcohol, Glycerin, Aloe Barbadensis leaf juice (Aloe Vera), Benzyl Alcohol\/Dehydroacetic Acid\/Sorbic Acid\/Benzoic Acid, Retinol\/ Adenosine\/Hydroxypropyl Cyclodextrin (Retinol A-vitamin), Furcellaria Lumbricalis extract (Furcellaran), Haematococcus pluvialis\/AstaZine (Astaxanthin oil)\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe glass bottle and pump system are reusable.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFree from parabens, silicones, mineral oils, synthetic flavours and colourants. Cruelty free and vegan. Suitable for sensitive and allergic skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Berrichi","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51042345550151,"sku":null,"price":33.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/berrichi-age-defence-night-cream-30ml-754136.png?v=1739897185"},{"product_id":"berrichi-light-natural-glow-cream-30ml","title":"BERRICHI Light Natural Glow Cream 30ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eDiscover Berrichi face cream Light – natural radiance and balance for your skin. Face cream Light is a light and silky cream designed to moisturise and protect combination and normal skin on a daily basis. It helps to restore the skin’s natural moisture balance, evens the texture and supports the skin’s natural defences, leaving skin radiant and soft.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBerrichi Light Natural Glow Cream:\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eLight and fast-absorbing texture that does not clog pores\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDeep moisturising action that restores the skin’s moisture balance\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSoothes irritations and soothes inflamed skin\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSmoothes the skin tone, reducing wrinkles and pigmentation.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAnti-ageing\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eMain ingredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cu\u003eFurcellaran\u003cstrong\u003e \u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/u\u003e– antioxidant, helps to maintain skin moisture balance and strengthen the skin’s protective barrier, slows down the skin’s ageing process, reduces inflammation and dryness. Furtsellaran is obtained from algae grown in Estonian waters.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eAstaxanthin\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e– an antioxidant, the most effective natural anti-ageing agent with the ability to penetrate cell membranes, affecting the skin deeply. Stimulates the production of collagen, balances the skin’s moisture levels, protects the skin from central irritants.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eAloe Vera\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e– antioxidant, antibacterial and anti-inflammatory properties that accelerate healing, moisturise the skin and prevent ageing.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eRough Razor Beard\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e– with antibacterial properties, it helps soothe and protect the skin, promoting a smoother, brighter complexion.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFor combined and normal skin\u003c\/span\u003e. Recommended for age 25+\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply to clean skin or over serum. Suitable as a foundation for make-up, it can also be used at night.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Persea Gratissima oil (Organic Avocado Oil)*, Prunus Armeniaca kernel oil (Organic Apricot kernel oil)*, Caryodendron Orinocense seed oil (Cacay Oil), Simmondsia Chinesis seed oil (Organic Jojoba oil)*, Cetearyl Olivate\/Sorbitan Olivate (Olivem1000), Cetearyl Alcohol, Glycerin**, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice\/Potassium Sorbate\/Sodium Benzoate\/Citric acid (Aloe Vera), Dehydroacetic Acid\/Benzoic Acid\/Benzyl Alcohol\/Sorbic Acid (Sharomix705), Helianthus Annuus Seed oil\/Polyglyceryl-3 Palmitate\/Usnea Barbata extract (Usnea Barbata), Furcellaria Lumbricalis extract (Furcellaran), Haemotococcus pluvialis\/Tocopherol (Astaxanthin oil)\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*Ingredients from organic farming\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003e**Made using organic ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe glass bottle and pump system are reusable.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFree from parabens, silicones, mineral oils, synthetic flavours and colourants. Cruelty free and vegan. Suitable for sensitive and allergic skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Berrichi","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51042379202887,"sku":null,"price":30.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/berrichi-light-natural-glow-cream-30ml-286537.png?v=1739897155"},{"product_id":"berrichi-age-defence-night-cream-refill-30ml","title":"BERRICHI Age Defence Night Cream REFILL 30ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eBerrichi night cream Night works for your skin while you rest. Rich and deeply hydrating, this night cream helps the skin to recover and recover from the day’s challenges, leaving it looking fresh and rested in the morning. It nourishes, hydrates and slows the signs of ageing, leaving skin more supple and plump.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBerrichi  Age Defence Night Cream:\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNourishes and restores, making the skin stronger and more resistant\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSoothes irritated and inflamed skin\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDeep moisturizing effect that keeps the skin soft and supple\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eEvens skin tone, reducing fine lines and wrinkles\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eStimulates blood circulation, helping the skin to regenerate faster\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eMain ingredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eFurcellaran \u003c\/span\u003e– antioxidant, helps to maintain skin moisture balance and strengthen the skin’s protective barrier, slows down the skin’s ageing process, reduces inflammation and dryness. Furtsellaran is obtained from algae grown in Estonian waters.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eAstaxanthin\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e– an antioxidant, the most effective natural anti-ageing agent with the ability to penetrate cell membranes, affecting the skin deeply. Stimulates the production of collagen, balances the skin’s moisture levels, protects the skin from central irritants.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eRetinol\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e– improves skin texture, increases radiance and acts against signs of aging. Retinol accelerates cell healing and skin renewal, increases collagen production, while smoothing out unevenness\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eAloe Vera\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e– antioxidant, antibacterial and anti-inflammatory properties that accelerate healing, moisturise the skin and prevent ageing.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eCacay oil\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e– rich in vitamins A and E. Helps reduce wrinkles and improve skin elasticity, stimulating collagen production and cell renewal.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e Suitable for all skin types\u003c\/span\u003e. Recommended for age 25+\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply to clean skin or apply serum. Use only as a night cream because it contains retinol. The effect of retinol is deactivated by the sun and can make the skin more sensitive to the sun.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Persea Gratissima oil (Organic Avocado oil), Prunus Armeniaca kernel oil (Organic Apricot kernel oil), Caryodendron Orinocense seed oil (Cacay oil), Aleurites Moluccana seed oil (Kukui nut oil), Cetearyl Olivate\/Sorbitan Olivate, Cetearyl Alcohol, Glycerin, Aloe Barbadensis leaf juice (Aloe Vera), Benzyl Alcohol\/Dehydroacetic Acid\/Sorbic Acid\/Benzoic Acid, Retinol\/ Adenosine\/Hydroxypropyl Cyclodextrin (Retinol A-vitamin), Furcellaria Lumbricalis extract (Furcellaran), Haematococcus pluvialis\/AstaZine (Astaxanthin oil)\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFree from parabens, silicones, mineral oils, synthetic flavours and colourants. Cruelty free and vegan. Suitable for sensitive and allergic skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Berrichi","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51084294717767,"sku":null,"price":25.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/berrichi-age-defence-night-cream-refill-30ml-277446.png?v=1739979948"},{"product_id":"berrichi-light-natural-glow-cream-refill-30ml","title":"BERRICHI Light Natural Glow Cream REFILL 30ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eDiscover Berrichi face cream Light – natural radiance and balance for your skin. Face cream Light is a light and silky cream designed to moisturise and protect combination and normal skin on a daily basis. It helps to restore the skin’s natural moisture balance, evens the texture and supports the skin’s natural defences, leaving skin radiant and soft.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBerrichi Light Natural Glow Cream:\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eLight and fast-absorbing texture that does not clog pores\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDeep moisturising action that restores the skin’s moisture balance\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSoothes irritations and soothes inflamed skin\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSmoothes the skin tone, reducing wrinkles and pigmentation.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAnti-ageing\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eMain ingredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cu\u003eFurcellaran\u003cstrong\u003e \u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/u\u003e– antioxidant, helps to maintain skin moisture balance and strengthen the skin’s protective barrier, slows down the skin’s ageing process, reduces inflammation and dryness. Furtsellaran is obtained from algae grown in Estonian waters.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eAstaxanthin\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e– an antioxidant, the most effective natural anti-ageing agent with the ability to penetrate cell membranes, affecting the skin deeply. Stimulates the production of collagen, balances the skin’s moisture levels, protects the skin from central irritants.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eAloe Vera\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e– antioxidant, antibacterial and anti-inflammatory properties that accelerate healing, moisturise the skin and prevent ageing.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eRough Razor Beard\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e– with antibacterial properties, it helps soothe and protect the skin, promoting a smoother, brighter complexion.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFor combined and normal skin\u003c\/span\u003e. Recommended for age 25+\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply to clean skin or over serum. Suitable as a foundation for make-up, it can also be used at night.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Persea Gratissima oil (Organic Avocado Oil)*, Prunus Armeniaca kernel oil (Organic Apricot kernel oil)*, Caryodendron Orinocense seed oil (Cacay Oil), Simmondsia Chinesis seed oil (Organic Jojoba oil)*, Cetearyl Olivate\/Sorbitan Olivate (Olivem1000), Cetearyl Alcohol, Glycerin**, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice\/Potassium Sorbate\/Sodium Benzoate\/Citric acid (Aloe Vera), Dehydroacetic Acid\/Benzoic Acid\/Benzyl Alcohol\/Sorbic Acid (Sharomix705), Helianthus Annuus Seed oil\/Polyglyceryl-3 Palmitate\/Usnea Barbata extract (Usnea Barbata), Furcellaria Lumbricalis extract (Furcellaran), Haemotococcus pluvialis\/Tocopherol (Astaxanthin oil)\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*Ingredients from organic farming\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003e**Made using organic ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFree from parabens, silicones, mineral oils, synthetic flavours and colourants. Cruelty free and vegan. Suitable for sensitive and allergic skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Berrichi","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51084305465671,"sku":null,"price":24.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/berrichi-light-natural-glow-cream-refill-30ml-453681.png?v=1739979948"}],"url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/collections\/ookreem.oembed","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}